OL,3,CGuernsey's Deputy Chief Minister
OL,4,Cavoids suspension
OL,6,FPoliticians have voted not to suspend
OL,7,FGuernsey's Deputy Chief Minister over
OL,8,Fa phone call with a national newspaper
OL,9,Fjournalist.
OL,11,FDeputy Gavin St Pier, the Vice-
OL,12,FPresident of Policy and Resources, was
OL,13,Ffound to have broken the States' Code
OL,14,Fof Conduct for talking to a Guardian
OL,15,Freporter about families' safeguarding
OL,16,Fcomplaints related to local Dr Sandie
OL,17,FBohin.
