OL,3,CGuernsey's Deputy Chief Minister
OL,4,Cavoids suspension
OL,6,FThe States' independent Commissioner
OL,7,Ffor Standards, Dr Melissa McCullough,
OL,8,Fsays independent reviews "have
OL,9,Fconsistently found no wrongdoing
OL,10,Frelated to Dr Bohin's clinical
OL,11,Fjudgement or her actions" and the
OL,12,Fallegations are "extremely serious and
OL,13,Funfounded".
OL,15,FThe Commissioner subsequently
OL,16,Frecommended that Deputy St Pier be
OL,17,Fsuspended for 25 days without pay.
