OL,3,CGuernsey's Deputy Chief Minister
OL,4,Cavoids suspension
OL,6,FSpeaking in the Assembly, Deputy St
OL,7,FPier said: "Firstly, it is my
OL,8,Freputation and integrity on the line `
OL,9,Fwhich, as Deputy Vermeulen has
OL,10,Facknowledged, is important.
OL,12,F"To the families who have been left
OL,13,Ffeeling powerless, unheard, and
OL,14,Fabandoned by the very system meant to
OL,15,Fhelp them and for which we are
OL,16,Fresponsible, I am deeply sorry.
OL,18,F"A number of them are in the gallery
OL,19,Ftoday, and I say to them: I am sorry
OL,20,Fthat your experiences have been
OL,21,Frepeatedly minimised and delegitimised.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
