OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1764271836
OL,3,CGuernsey's Deputy Chief Minister
OL,4,Cavoids suspension
OL,6,F"Those families who raised and those
OL,7,Fwho continue to come forward to raise
OL,8,Ftheir concerns, their dissatisfaction,
OL,9,Ftheir complaints, have done so in good
OL,10,Ffaith."
OL,12,FClosing his speech, he added: "Whether
OL,13,Fthe States endorses or rejects the
OL,14,Frecommended sanction, I promise you
OL,15,Fthis: I will not stop fighting, not
OL,16,Fjust for change, but for a future
OL,17,Fwhere no parent and no patient feels
OL,18,Fsilenced, and every family knows they
OL,19,Fwill be heard."
