OL,6,FFollowing the decision, Dr Steve
OL,7,FEvans, Chair of Guernsey's Medical
OL,8,FSpecialist Group (MSG) which employs
OL,9,FDr Bohin and backed the suspension,
OL,10,Fsaid: "I'm obviously disappointed that
OL,11,Fthe politicians didn't support the
OL,12,Fconclusions of the independent Code of
OL,13,FConduct Commissioner, but what we need
OL,14,Fto do is move on in a positive way if
OL,15,Fwe can.
