OL,6,F"The MSG and HSC (Health and Social
OL,7,FCare) need to continue to provide care
OL,8,Ffor families on the island. What we
OL,9,Fneed to do is make sure that people do
OL,10,Frealise that both HSC and MSG are open
OL,11,Fto complaints, and they are
OL,12,Finvestigated clearly and fairly, and
OL,13,Fwe learn from the outcomes."
